        Don't let the inspected page overwrite properties of JS objects in the
        Inspector

        <https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=16011>
        <rdar://problem/5604409>

        <https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=16837>
